data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. LARGE PRICE REDUCTION.....MOTIVATED SELLERS..........Location location location!!!!! WOW..... This SPECTACULAR 3/4 bed 2 bath home is located within minutes to HWY 27 and HWY 50 making life simple to get to ALL Theme Parks and Attractions including plentiful shopping, restaurants,Schools,parks, churches and Theater and much more.   The subdivision has "Lake Access to the Clermont Chain of Lakes with a private beach", dock, boat ramp and picnic area.   As you enter the spacious grounds of this delightful home you will feel the warmth and welcoming feeling for all to enjoy.OH.... AND INCLUDED IS : NEW APPLIANCES,NEW METAL ROOF,NEW INTERIOR PAINT, GORGEOUS NEW INTERIOR LIGHTING,NEW OUTLETS THROUGHOUT THE HOME, NEW BIGGER WINDOWS GIVING MORE NATURAL LIGHT, NEW EPOXY ON GARAGE FLOOR, NEW IRRIGATION SYSTEM, NEW AC FOR THE BEDROOM.     A stone wood burning fireplace, a newly remodeled kitchen with granite countertops, an outdoor covered  gazebo with metal roof too , and a  storage shed with power.  The Home is fenced all round giving privacy. Mature landscaping both front and back . Fruit trees including Papaya and lemon and avacado and more.  Don't miss out and schedule your showing today. It's a hidden gem.
